[Arch Rivals Codes\Player 1 Always Shoots at Basket Modifier]
author=BigBossman
description=Modifies between making the player shoot at either the left or right basket, even after halftime. 
Values - 
00 - Right Basket
01 - Left Basket
patch=1,EE,008739EA,extended,00000000

[Arch Rivals Codes\Player 1 Ball in Possession Modifier]
author=BigBossman
description=This will modify whether or not the player is in possession of the ball. It is possible for more than one player to be in possession of the ball. However, it will make things a bit confusing. It also makes performing 3-Point shots more difficult & might even be glitchy at times. Performing slam dunks is the best way to score, when this code is active. Also, making it to where nobody is in possession of the ball, will make the screen stay in one place, & eventually activate the shot clock. These codes might best be used with a joker code.
Values - 
00 - Player is never in possession of the ball
01 - Player is always in possession of the ball
patch=1,EE,00873A24,extended,00000000

[Arch Rivals Codes\Player 1 Character Modifier]
author=BigBossman
description=Values -
00 - Tyrone
01 - Vinnie
02 - Hammer
03 - Moose
04 - Lewis
05 - Blade
06 - Mohawk
07 - Reggie
patch=1,EE,008739E6,extended,00000000

[Primal Rage Codes\Player 1 Control Modifier]
author=BigBossman
description=If the CPU controlled Player 1 beats the CPU controlled Player 2, it will go to the continue screen & ask Player 2 to continue. If the countdown goes to 0, then Player 1 will take on the same CPU Controlled Player 2 opponent with the same result after the win.
Values -
00 - Player
01 - CPU
patch=1,EE,006263EB,extended,00000000

[Primal Rage Codes\Player 1 is Never Stunned]
author=BigBossman
description=
patch=1,EE,106263E4,extended,00000000

