patch=1,EE,105A5342,extended,00000011

[Pit-Fighter Codes\Player 1 Modifier]
author=BigBossman
description=Freezes between stages when using values "03" or higher. Values go beyond what's listed. 0B & beyond will find different colored characters. Needs a Joker Code.
Values - 
00 - Buzz
01 - Ty
02 - Kato
03 - Chainman
04 - South Side
05 - Masked Warrior
06 - Mad Miles
07 - CC Rider 
08 - Executioner
09 - Heavy Metal
0A - Angel
patch=1,EE,112439D4,extended,00000000

[Primal Rage Codes\Player 1 Modifier]
author=BigBossman
description=Values - 
00 - Sauron 
01 - Blizzard
02 - Talon
03 - Vertigo
04 - Armaddon
05 - Diablo 
06 - Chaos
07 - Glitches & Freezes
patch=1,EE,00626402,extended,00000000

[Arch Rivals Codes\Player 1's Jersey & Skin Color Modifier]
author=BigBossman
description=This code will change your jersey color to your opponent's or your selected team's color. Changing the values will also modify the player's skin color too.
patch=1,EE,008739E8,extended,00000000

